- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper deals with forecasting the flow of crowds, which is of great importance to traffic management and public safety, and involves analyzing the complex factors that affect crowd traffic. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep-learning-based approach for forecasting crowd flows, which involves designing an end-to-end structure of ST-ResNet based on unique properties of spatio-temporal data.
